room_title: Escape room "Pirate Captives" by 11th Hour Escape in Corpus Christi
room_address: 4455 S Padre Island Dr #105, Corpus Christi, TX 78411
room_description:
Blimey! Your ship has been taken captive and you end up locked in the brig! Your pirate captors will let you become part of the crew… if you prove yourself and solve your way out. Try to cheat or don’t make it out in time and you’ll walk the plank, matey.
Your group can choose the level of difficulty: easy (50% success rate), medium (25%) or hard (10%).
